                  <decoDesc>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1"><locus target="#ir" facs="001">Fol. ir</locus><desc>drawings of two churches</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#iir" facs="002">Fol. iir</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1035HolyMan">Holy Man Portrait</ref>, seated with a book (an Evangelist?)</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#iiir" facs="003">Fol. iiir</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1035HolyMan">Holy Man Portrait</ref> standing standing in an archway flanked by two <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1041HolyMen">Holy Men Potrait</ref></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4"><locus target="#iiiv" facs="004">Fol. iiiv</locus><desc>Two <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1041HolyMen">Holy Men Potrait</ref> standing with arms crossed</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d5"><locus target="#1r" facs="004">Fol. 1r</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1002Annunciation">Annunciation</ref></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d6"><locus target="#9r" facs="012">Fol. 9r</locus><desc>Two <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1041HolyMen">Holy Men Potrait</ref> standing with arms crossed</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d7"><locus target="#42v" facs="046">Fol. 42v</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1005Crucifixion">Crucifixion of Jesus</ref> with two male figures standing on either side of the cross</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d8"><locus target="#45v" facs="049">Fol. 45v</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1035HolyMan">Holy Man Portrait</ref>,<persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4585Georgeo">St George of Lydda</persName> and the <term key="dragon" ana="#dragon"/></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d9"><locus target="#89v" facs="093">Fol. 89v</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1031VirginAndChild">Virgin and Child</ref> with two <term key="angel" ana="#angel"/></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d10"><locus target="#91r" facs="094">Fol. 91r</locus>A standing <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1035HolyMan">Holy Man Portrait</ref> (<desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1084JesusChrist">JesusChrist</ref>?) with two <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1041HolyMen">Holy Men Potrait</ref> kneeling and touching his garment</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d11"><locus target="#92v" facs="096">Fol. 92v</locus><desc>Two <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1082Angel">Angel</ref></desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d12">
                      Decorative designs:
                      <locus target="#1r #44r" facs="004 047">folss. 1r, 44r, </locus>, ornamental band;
                      <locus target="#1r #4r #6r #13v #51v" facs="004 007 009 017 055">1r, 4r, 6r, 13v, 51v, </locus>, lines of alternating red and black dots;
                      <locus target="#41v #72v #81r #85r #88v #89r" facs="045 076 084 088 092">41v, 72v, 81r, 85r, 88v, 89r</locus>, lines of black dots</decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                    <list>
                      <item xml:id="e1"><desc>The quires are wrapped with a spine strap, <locus target="#i #92" facs="001 096">fols. i, 92</locus>.</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="e2"><desc><locus target="#iv #90r #90v #92r #92v" facs="002 093 094 095 096">Fols. iv, 90r, 90v, 92r, 92v</locus> blank.</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a1"><desc><locus target="#13r" facs="016">Fol. 13r</locus> mentions <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7006Menilek">Mǝnilǝk</persName></desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a2"><desc><locus target="#21v #23v" facs="025 027">Fols. 21v, 23v</locus> mentions <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6404Luqas">Luqas</persName> and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6876Matewos">Mātewos X</persName></desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a3"><desc><locus target="#23v" facs="027">Fol. 23v</locus> mentions the death of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6404Luqas">Luqas</persName></desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="a4"><desc><locus target="#24r" facs="027">Fol. 24r</locus> mentions <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6876Matewos">Mātewos X</persName></desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="e3"><desc><locus target="#51v" facs="055">Fol. 51v</locus> space for the name of the owner is left blank</desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="e4"><desc>The headings in red ink stop after <locus target="#61v" facs="064">fols. 61v, </locus> and the space for them in subsequent folios is left blank. The lone exception is the heading on f<locus target="#89r" facs="092">89r</locus></desc></item>
                      <item xml:id="e5"><desc>
                        Scribal intervention: words of text are written interlinearly <locus target="#4v #5v #10r #13r #13v" facs="008 009 013 016 017">fols. 4v, 5v, 10r, 13r, 13v</locus>, etc.</desc></item>
                    </list>
                  </additions>

                  <bindingDesc>
                    <binding xml:id="binding" contemporary="partly">
                      <decoNote xml:id="b1">Parchment, four Coptic chain stitches attached with bridle attachments to rough-hewn boards of the traditional wood, both covers have been broken and repaired.</decoNote>
                      <decoNote xml:id="b2" type="bindingMaterial">
                        <material key="parchment"/>
                        <material key="wood"/>
                      </decoNote>
                    </binding>
                  </bindingDesc>
